    writer {
      name: "Ivan Raimi"
    }
    rating: "Bad"
    comments: "The plot is not that great because it introduces too many characters, it has 3 villains and a new love interest, and only increases the runtime by 10 minutes, so the structure is just mismanaged and breezes through plot points; the character writing is a step back because it introduces too many characters and does not provide any depth to them"
  }
